# JavaScript Calculator

## Description
This project is a simple calculator built using JavaScript. It performs basic arithmetic operations and stores a history of calculations.

## Features
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division
- Handles string inputs using Number()
- Stores calculation history
- Clear history function

## How to Run
1. Open terminal
2. Run: node calculator.js

## Example
calculate(5, "+", 3) → 8